Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96659,98369}Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98369,99829}Good morning, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99829,101789}Another lovely day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:43.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101789,103166}It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:51.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108338,111132}Seira, what's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111132,116137}Maybe Asuka Jr.'s solved a case\Nand they want his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116137,118139}That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122143,125521}Yutaka, please!\NGet your father to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126105,129484}But my father's not even an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130401,133071}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:18.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133071,138868}Didn't you know?\NYutaka's father wrote a bestseller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139327,142955}Oh, really? Seira, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142955,146834}I bought one. It's titled\NExpedition Journal of Jurassic Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:32.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147502,152048}His father discovered an egg\Nof the legendary bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153174,154801}A legendary bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.01,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:156761,160014}Get Back The Phantom Bird Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164435,166562}Seira, have you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166562,169732}Yes, would you like to read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:55.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170817,175822}It looks so hard.\NMaybe I'll just go get his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:01.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176531,181744}Professor Mochizuki, Yutaka's father,\Nis a well-known explorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:09.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182578,189168}He was investigating the existence of the bird\Nin a jungle in the southern hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189794,192171}And he discovered the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192797,198094}Yes. A fiery red Apua bird said\Nto have lived on the island ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198094,201097}Then he compiled\Nhis report into a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201514,204976}Exploring a jungle, a fiery red bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204976,207228}How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214360,216529}A lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:42.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218364,222243}You'll never go exploring the jungle\Nif this little thing scares you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234422,238509}Mr. Asuka, pets are not allowed\Nin the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238509,242346}As punishment, you will clean\Nthe birdcage after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245516,247018}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257987,260364}Your father's precious egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260823,262033}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262033,265244}Professor Hyuga from the\NScientific Research Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265244,268623}came by, claiming\Nto be my father's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:36.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271959,276339}I'd appreciate you letting me\Nborrow your father's egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276339,280635}My father's not in tonight.\NCan you wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281302,283971}I have his permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:50.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283971,290645}I'd like to study the egg as part\Nof my research of the Apua bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290645,293815}Why, I promise to return it\Nin two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:59.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294273,299070}{\i1}He said he'd return it and I let him\Ntake it without thinking it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299654,303032}What? Hyuga took\Nthe egg last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303699,306661}Oh, God, I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306661,307995}Dad, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:14.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310289,314877}Yutaka, I made the egg. It's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314877,317964}I painted an ostrich egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318673,322677}Then you lied\Nabout discovering the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322677,325680}You wrote that book\Nbased on pure fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326180,329475}No, I'm certain\NI really did find the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329475,332520}Animals are very delicate creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:39.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333104,339151}Being tossed around on a long ocean voyage\Nto Japan would kill any animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:43.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339151,343114}That egg is priceless,\Nso I didn't bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343114,346075}I wanted the bird to be raised there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346075,347034}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:52.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347493,352957}But I had to let the world\Nknow of my discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:57.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352957,357879}I needed proof\Nto convince my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:03.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358838,363426}So you made the fake\Nto use as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:08.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363426,368639}But I never imagined my book\Nwould cause such a sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:14.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368639,374312}A man in my position should never have\Nused a fake to prove his discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374312,377356}Then why don't you explain it\Nto everyone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378024,381027}You're right.\NBut of all the bad luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381027,383237}it will be Hyuga\Nwho breaks the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387283,388743}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:34.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389577,394373}Professor Hyuga has always\Ncriticized my father's research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:39.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394373,399420}If he analyzes the egg,\Nhe's sure to realize it's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399420,401881}I need the egg back before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401881,404842}And where is the egg now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404842,407428}Hyuga's Scientific Research Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410306,411933}A fake egg, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:57.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412767,417772}Using a fake to prove one's theory\Nis certainly unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:02.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417772,422026}But Professor Mochizuki\Ndeeply regrets it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:06.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422818,426364}And it's too bad Professor Hyuga\Nwill reveal the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:11.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427281,431118}I did some checking and learned\Nthat Professor Hyuga…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:15.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431118,435081}…is scheduled to go on TV\Ntomorrow to discuss the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435665,437124}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:21.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437124,441087}You want me to get the egg\Nbefore he analyzes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441462,444465}Brilliant deduction.\NI knew I could count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:34.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448636,454433}Why did she have to stick me\Nwith this dirty job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456560,459438}I need to clean this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462233,464443}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466404,467488}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467488,470574}"Tonight at 8:00, I am going\Nto Professor Hyuga's lab
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470574,473911}to steal the legendary egg.\N– St. Tail".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473911,476122}A note from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481252,483337}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483337,484630}Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485006,487633}What's with Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492847,495141}Hi, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495850,497518}Oh, Meimi, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:23.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498227,503649}What's the matter? You promised\Nto show me your trick when I got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503649,507069}I'm sorry. I got so involved\Nwith the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507069,508362}What program?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.82,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:508362,513826}Uncover paranormal phenomena\Nwith Dr. Hyuga
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509697,511198}Dr. Hyuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511198,513826}– You know him?\N– Yeah, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:40.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514452,520374}You were saying there is nothing\Nthat is scientifically unexplainable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520374,521667}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:47.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521667,527965}Supernatural phenomena and legendary\Ncreatures do not exist in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527965,531844}For example, mirages\Nand a dead person's spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:57.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531844,537475}which so many romanticize about,\Nhave been scientifically explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538559,541353}This is a mirage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541353,546650}Isn't it incredible? Even a machine\Nis capable of creating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546650,548611}And now, to continue…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548611,549779}A dead person's spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:18.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552156,558287}Lately, I've been hearing of fools\Ncausing a sensation by ranting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558287,561707}of miracles and legends,\Nbut I will expose them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561707,562500}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562500,565669}This journal is a bestseller, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:26.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565669,566837}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566837,570841}In my professional opinion,\Nthe legendary Apua bird
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:35.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570841,575012}does not exist anywhere.\NThis book is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575304,579475}And tomorrow on this program,\Nwe will reveal the infamous egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:45.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582103,585981}The egg Professor Mochizuki found\Ncannot be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585981,588442}And I will expose—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588901,590069}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590069,592530}Why'd you turn it off?\NIt was interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593072,596826}Because I don't like that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596826,600246}The other day at a magic show,\Nthat awful man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600246,602748}revealed the secrets\Nin front of the magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603666,606961}Then he's one of Dad's enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:11.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606961,611215}That's right. Without the world's\Nmysteries and magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611215,612967}there'd be no dreams or hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:19.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613759,619056}You're right. Eimi, I appreciate\Nyou always thinking of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619056,621183}Oh, dear, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625271,627773}Oh, brother, here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630693,632444}Hi, Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634572,638659}I've got work to do. I'll play\Nwith you in just a little while.
Comment: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:40.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:640661,640661}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:46.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:646667,646667}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:51.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:651672,651672}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:58.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654592,658429}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663392,664435}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666854,668105}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670232,672443}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685873,689168}Meimi, you have to be\Nextra careful this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689627,691253}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:37.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691253,697885}I've heard Professor Hyuga has a state-of-the-art\Nsecurity system wired in his laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698552,702181}It just makes the job\Nmore challenging for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704391,707853}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:58.94,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:714235,718948}Hyuga Scientific Research Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714777,718948}I appreciate you reporters\Ncoming out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:05.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721033,725412}Professor Hyuga, there are reports\NSt. Tail has announced—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725746,728540}I don't know about any St. Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:14.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728540,734630}but my computers will capture\Nany brash, petty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735297,737800}Well, just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:34.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749478,754608}You seem to be my personal bodyguards,\Nbut I told you, I don't need your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755526,758612}You're not taking St. Tail\Nvery seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758612,761323}If she says she's coming, she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:46.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761782,766662}Detective, I appreciate your concern,\Nbut I want you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766662,768789}I have enough help here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769206,770749}We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:55.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770749,775754}Since she has made her announcement,\Nit is our duty to arrest her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776005,782094}This laboratory has been equipped with\Nthe latest computers I've invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782094,785597}When it comes to police intuition\Nor experience…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785597,788309}…I just don't believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:13.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788309,793605}That is your prerogative, but\Nour job is to stand guard right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793605,795107}Have it your way then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795691,798777}That door is unlocked, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:23.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798777,803073}St. Tail can easily enter from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:30.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804283,810372}As part of my plan,\NI'm letting St. Tail get in easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810372,814793}I will capture her alive and then\Nmy secret weapon will go into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815336,816670}Secret weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818213,820883}And this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.38,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:820883,822384}I am a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825804,826889}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827973,829391}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831727,835356}These will not kill or hurt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:59.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835356,839610}It's like a tranquilizer gun\Nfor live capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:03.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840110,843322}That's quite impressive.\NAnd what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843322,846575}Oh, that.\NThat's the character analyzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847242,849203}It looks like it'll fry someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:14.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849620,854583}Shall I demonstrate it?\NYou just stand there quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868097,871850}Daisuke Asuka. Born August 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871850,874645}Horoscope: Leo. Blood type: AB.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:40.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875145,880401}Fantastic! It analyzes one's personal\Ndata just by shining a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880401,883946}Does that mean\Nif the light hits St. Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883946,886365}we'll learn her true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886698,891412}That's right. Today's the day\Nwe learn her true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891412,893831}Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:59.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894498,899211}Just in case, I'm going\Nto tape St. Tail's capture
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899211,902047}and have it shown on national TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902714,904299}{\i1}What a showoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904633,908429}If I am unable to capture her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908429,912266}I will shave my head completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921692,923735}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931743,933036}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933036,934913}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935581,938208}We've got you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938208,940586}Assistants A, B, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943630,945924}Here I am! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950304,952389}Drat! Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953557,955309}She'll never be able to get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955309,957311}Not here, at any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961023,963901}You idiot!\NWhat are you shooting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963901,965986}You call this gun safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969781,971074}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973160,974870}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977080,979458}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983212,985214}What are these things? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988050,989510}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992721,993472}Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995224,997184}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000938,1004149}Damn! I'll reveal her identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006276,1007653}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013116,1014785}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016745,1018372}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024002,1025837}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038642,1040894}Stop, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040894,1042604}I'll let you go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:27.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042604,1047192}But only because I don't want\Nto capture you with machinery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047192,1048986}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:38.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054783,1058745}– Professor! Professor!\N– The egg, the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059079,1061915}Professor, snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:45.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061915,1065419}What was I doing? That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:50.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065419,1070924}I'm sure my computer grasped\NSt. Tail's true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070924,1072759}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073302,1075721}St. Tail's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076388,1077973}Everything's in order!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082019,1083478}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083812,1085939}It's all white.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:11.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088275,1091278}Hey, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094239,1097534}This is one of those pebbles\NSt. Tail threw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097534,1098994}What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098994,1100412}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101913,1105250}Hey! Dad, isn't this a magnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105250,1108712}I get it. These machines\Ndon't take to magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:34.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109087,1114926}That's ridiculous!\NBut the video should show her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:45.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118889,1125020}My machines of the latest technology\Nwere thwarted by mere magnets. Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129858,1130942}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:01.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137366,1141953}What's this?\NDad, it's the egg! The egg's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141953,1143914}What… What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145749,1146375}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148543,1152339}Yutaka, I'm going to make\Na public apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153340,1155175}About the egg being a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:20.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155717,1160514}Yes, and I'll ask everyone to help\Npreserve the island's natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161390,1162099}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165894,1167729}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168605,1170774}– Good morning!\N– Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173151,1176029}Professor Mochizuki\Nwas so very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180075,1182244}Good morning, Meimi, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182244,1184037}We'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184621,1187374}– Please let us through!\N– Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188583,1190961}Congratulations! I saw the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190961,1195841}The Apua bird's egg on\NJurassic Island hatched, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:20:00.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196758,1200303}It's so neat! Please get me\Nyour father's autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200679,1202305}Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.26,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1205767,1207269}Dr. Hyuga went bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211565,1213316}Good morning, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213316,1215485}Did you see this?\NLook at that bald fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:22.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217154,1222951}A bet's a bet. And he bet he could\Nreveal St. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:27.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223535,1227914}I guess that means capturing St. Tail\Nshould be left to you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:33.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228749,1233628}That's right, because I'm the best.\NI know everything about St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233628,1235922}Though she's always getting away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:40.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236339,1240177}What did you say? I had a good reason\Nfor letting her go this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241303,1242387}{\i1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246600,1250145}{\i1}You said, "I don't want\Nto capture you with machinery!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250145,1252272}{\i1}And you work so hard at it!
